---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About DevToolKit — Free Developer Tools" description="DevToolKit is a collection of free, fast, privacy-first developer tools built with AstroJS.">
  <Header />
  <div class="container static-page-container">
    <h1>About DevToolKit</h1>
    <p>DevToolKit is a free, open-source collection of developer tools built by developers, for developers. Every tool runs entirely in your browser — your data never touches our servers.</p>
    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
    <p>We believe developer tools should be free, fast, and private. No accounts, no tracking, no data harvesting. Just useful utilities that help you get your work done.</p>
    <h2>Tech Stack</h2>
    <p>DevToolKit is built with modern, performance-first technologies:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>AstroJS</strong> — Zero JavaScript by default for blazing-fast page loads</li>
      <li><strong>Cloudflare Pages</strong> — Global CDN with edge caching for instant access worldwide</li>
      <li><strong>Client-Side Processing</strong> — All tools run in your browser, keeping your data private</li>
    </ul>
    <h2>Open Source</h2>
    <p>DevToolKit is open source. You can submit feedback and feature requests via <a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Forms</a>!</p>
    <h2>Contact & Feedback</h2>
    <p>Have a suggestion or found a bug? Submit feedback via <a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Forms</a>.</p>
  </div>
  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
